{"tid":1583028,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"被禁的顏色 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-09-20T11:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T11:36:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"618495a89c230fd898897d1900aed428fac73363","tid":1583028,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190920/20771321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771321&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG194xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=113cf8d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771321&h=5c08b44e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190920/20771321</a><br />\n<br />\n被禁的顏色 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190920/large/1568887137_aa5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568887137_aa5f.jpg&h=c9e73f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有朋友打算印製一批「岳」字黑色T恤送給大家，純粹是喜歡「岳」字所代表的意義。這件山友之服，穿在一個少年身上，其守望相助、無私無畏的精神表露無遺。也形象地詮釋出兄弟爬山的真義，每個人用自己的方式爬山，目標一致。<br />\n<br />\n結果，以前幫襯開的公司不肯接單。不知是否生產商自我審查，只說有沒有印字都好，黑色T恤被禁止運港，黑色，居然成為禁色。<br />\n<br />\n自從凌烈士以死相諫，反修例遊行的服裝由白衫變成黑衫，用來紀念我們的失去：同行人寶貴的生命、眼睛、自由、終身健康&hellip;&hellip;也紀念香港失去的民主、自由、法治。<br />\n<br />\n黑衣人代表了良知，從7.21開始，屢屢成為被黑幫施襲、被警察捕捉、圍毆、濫暴的對象。麗晶花園的住戶更曾因為身穿黑衣被拒諸大廈鐵閘外，有家歸不得。<br />\n<br />\n短短三個月時間，香港變得面目全非。早三個月，如果有人說在香港，某一種顏色會成為禁色，相信所有的人都會捧腹大笑，或痛斥荒天下之大謬。可是今天，應該沒有人能笑得出來。因為我們的現狀確實變得比周星星電影更荒誕。早三個月，如果有女人因為貪靚，想讓自己的身材看上去纖瘦一些而穿黑衣，家人不會多口說，「放工早些回家，盡量選擇其他交通工具，穿黑色衫搭地鐵遇到警察會有危險。」 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n藍絲不是黑絲 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n法治呵呵呵 (古德明)"},{"pid":"eafb6738918ca2f511b68521d04d491e418e0f17","tid":1583028,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:32:15.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG194xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=5962c337\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG194xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=6cb68e51\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"67c248bdf3da409c8eab34cb7debfe9caffa4001","tid":1583028,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" d